resources.name: RPG Pack - Kenney.nl
resources.description:
Ready to create an RPG game? Let me help you out with a base set of RPG tiles covering everything from grass, dirt and water to buildings, roofs, windows and crates.

Stay tuned for expansions covering characters, monsters, building interiors and dungeons!

resources.name: Tanks Topdown
resources.description: This pack of assets includes 86 sprites. Tanks, barrels, sandbags, ground tiles, spilled oil, bullets, smoke/explosions, trees and tracks.Thanks to Kenney.nl for these great assets.
